{"tid":612033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[靈異]靈異jj麻煩入一入嚟","createTime":"2018-03-31T14:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T16:00:26.000Z","uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1b9379b9c35cea0147546171b5c65706d3af99","tid":612033,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"今日喺銅鑼灣行街<br />\n行咗上去金伯利12樓想買下嘢咁啦<br />\n點知一行到入某鋪頭嘅時候我即刻覺得個人好浮 頭好重暈暈哋好似畀嘢壓住 隻腳行唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好艱難先行到<br />\n究竟咁樣係咩情況 係感應到大量靈體定係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 : 冇病冇痛有足夠休息 唔係精神唔好嗰種暈，同埋平時喺返工嘅鋪頭見過好多朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後頭先翻到屋企阿媽話我面青口唇白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aadf5b6fe5b929e2b89a182cd6d17b55ff924f4","tid":612033,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467795b9b21a7ab1b9c2a50a01101bce8eee7d53","tid":612033,"uid":23895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:54:51.000Z","msg":"樓主有冇戴啲咩護身？"},{"pid":"332bbb6406a6cdb06337aa96a4687c1f39594454","tid":612033,"uid":56018,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"舖頭有人隊草你唔小心吸左"},{"pid":"57bee7b24f76da2f229e09bcb33ae58f7aefed34","tid":612033,"uid":49918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:56:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69e86f06192df501b9407db2bdded1b8cd6e86ea","tid":612033,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T15:04:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遇到大陸迷暈黨啫，好彩你入左鋪頭，唔係係街比人夾左上車就冇左個腎了</blockquote><br />\n但成層都冇其他客 得我兩個人同店員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3670e16cecd809aff14c355e1098d67d448e6532","tid":612033,"uid":108668,"like":0,"disl